{
  "stem": "22883.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because you know, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they-- they were always running ahead of us, but quite a distance.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we had to really run after them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You know, I had this impression that they are ashamed of being connected with us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You know, they were treating us like-- like lepers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, well, they were collaborating with Germans, and so-- and you know, the occupation of-- of Denmark was quite friendly.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So anyway.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we start-- well, I was quarreling with this company that I wanted to-- to-- to work as a designer or something like that, or-- but not as ordinary worker.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were trying to force me-- and of course, the point was that I didn't want to be separated from my wife, Lilian.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was a problem.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because all the workers, male, were living in one camp, and the-- the female. were living in another camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they wanted to separate us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were opposing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So anyway, there was a smaller room where the office of that company, of this Danish company, was there with beds.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So it's like-- like a kind of a motel, but for-- just for two people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we asked to-- that until they find us the occupation or employment in such a way that we could stay together, and of course, some-- some living quarters-- so we were using this.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So anyway, a few days, we were sleeping in this small room next to this office.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one-- there was-- I think it was next Sunday or something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We heard that the new transport of workers from Warsaw is coming to this company, to this Kapfenberg company.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So of course-- because we were sleeping there anyway.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
